text: Sven Jajcinovic (born 4 April 1993, Sisak, Croatia) is a Croatian footballer who plays as a midfielder. He joined Milsami on July 2016. He made his debut for Milsami on 23 July 2016 in a game against FC Saxan, Milsami won this game with 2-0. == External links == * Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:Croatian footballers Category:NK Hrvatski Dragovoljac players Category:Croatian First Football League players Category:Association football midfielders
